
start zookeeper
===============
bin\windows\zookeeper-server-start.bat config\zookeeper.properties

start kafka
=============
bin\windows\kafka-server-start.bat config\server.properties

kafka create topic
===================

bin\windows\kafka-topics.bat --create --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --replication-factor 1 --partitions 1 --topic myKafkaTest